Name: Average time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Total time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Average time between Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and SW-AE Assign Reviewers
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Total resolution time of Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time to Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Minimum time until Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation is performed after Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Total time it takes Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to be followed by Plagiarism Originality Report Completed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Average time for Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to lead to a decision (SW-EIC Reject, SW-EIC Major Revision, SW-EIC Minor Revision, SW-EIC Accept)
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-EIC Reject' or activity == 'SW-EIC Major Revision' or activity == 'SW-EIC Minor Revision' or activity == 'SW-EIC Accept'", 'aggregation': 'average'}

Name: Time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to the first Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: Time to Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation since the last activity in the manuscript submission process
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation Cycle Time in the context of the review process of scientific papers
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and the end of the case

Name: Average time it takes from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation in cases of major revisions
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Total time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation in successful submissions
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'
